snippet.title: Fast Fox App Promo Trailer
snippet.description:
The Fast Fox By Roi Ben David
Fast Fox is a game where you have to help the fox to reach the end of the road, without hitting obstacles on the way. You need to accumulate as many fruits as possible to move on to the next level.
AppStore: https://appsto.re/il/Ic3Wlb.i
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.roibendavid.fastfox
